headline: Palestinians say IDF invading Ramallah
description: Palestinian sources said that a number of IDF jeeps have entered the city center of Ramallah.  According to the report, Israel warned the Palestinian Authority to clear its security personnel from the area. (Ali Waked)
articleBody: Palestinian sources said that a number of IDF jeeps have entered the city center of Ramallah.  According to the report, Israel warned the Palestinian Authority to clear its security personnel from the area. (Ali Waked)
title: בסטודיו של מותג האופנה גוסטה: "מדמיינת ריזורט במזרח התיכון"
